## Web Enumeration (Port 80) ğŸŒğŸ§

Initial web enumeration focused on identifying common entry points.

- Manual inspection revealed no obvious uploads or injections  
- Automated enumeration was used to locate hidden paths  

At this stage, the web app alone did not provide direct access.

However, the provided hint made one thing clear:

ğŸ‘‰ **Web access is only the entry â€” kernel exploitation is the endgame.**

